==Introduction==
パスタの国が生んだ、新型戦艦向けに開発された最新鋭の高角砲です。
単砲身ではありますが、発射速度も速く、バランスのよい優れた中距離対空火器です。

''From the land of the pasta, this state of the art high angled gun was developed for the new battleships. It may only have a single barrel, but with its fast firing rate, this gun was able to perform well because of its well balanced mid-range anti air defenses.''

==Notes==
With regards to [[Aerial Combat#Anti-Air Cut-In|Anti-Air Cut-In]], it behaves like [[12.7cm Twin High-angle Mount + Anti-Aircraft Fire Director]] and [[5inch Twin Gun Mount Mk.28 mod.2]]; you only need an AA RADAR equipped with it to enable AACI.

